                                 <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> "A planned process by which defense acquisition capability requirements are determined (e.g. the legacy JCIDS or the reformed Joint Force Requirements Process)." ;
                                 rdfs:isDefinedBy <https://w3id.org/rockworx/acq> ;
                                 rdfs:label "Requirement Determination Process" ;
                                 <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A planned process by which defense acquisition capability requirements are determined (e.g. the legacy JCIDS or the reformed Joint Force Requirements Process)." .


